            <title>Version 1.8</title>
            <pubDate>Sat, 18 Jan 2026 17:50:00 +0000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>9</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.8</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>13.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>VibeStatus v1.8</h2>
                <h3>Terminal.app Compatibility</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Fixed detection issues when running Claude Code from Terminal.app</li>
                    <li>Improved process detection (case-insensitive, supports node process)</li>
                    <li>Increased process tree walk depth for deeper shell hierarchies</li>
                </ul>
                <h3>UI Improvements</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Sidebar tabs now fully clickable</li>
                    <li>Settings window uses black theme</li>
                    <li>Removed Auto Show/Hide toggle (always on by default)</li>
                </ul>
                <h3>Bug Fixes</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Fixed crash when changing widget style</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
